UI for Neti Neti Taxon Finder and Reconciliation tools

1) run py server for neti tf
2) run web service for neti tf (will move this one to common file)
3) run py server for reconciliation
4) run web service for reconciliation (will move this one to common file)
5) run ./names_tools.rb -p 3001

---------
Neti Neti TF (server/client - port 1234, service 4567):
1) run py server for neti tf
cd /Users/anna/work/web_app/perl_tf/py_server/
python L-server-test.py 

2) run web service for neti tf (will move this one to common file)
cd /Users/anna/work/web_app/perl_tf/webservices/ruby/
ruby taxon_finder_web_service.rb
----------
Reconciliation (server/client - port 3002, service 3000):
3) run py server for reconciliation
cd /Users/anna/work/sinatra/Web-Service-for-names-tools/py_server/ 
/py_server 8556$ python recons_server.py

4) run web service for reconciliation (will move this one to common file)
clear && ruby reconcile_web_service.rb -p 3000 
---------
5) run ./names_tools.rb -p 3001
ruby /Users/anna/work/sinatra/Web-Service-for-names-tools/sinatra/names_tools.rb -p 3001

